{"tid":1008300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【轉貼】毋忘義士  初一起義  4-FEB 9:00PM  旺角砵蘭街","createTime":"2019-02-04T11:17:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T12:56:21.000Z","uid":79563,"like":18,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d53f977698e6bf59f65f60d60abf3f19c4f37e4e","tid":1008300,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T11:17:57.000Z","msg":"FB: <a href=\"https://zh-hk.facebook.com/students.independence.union/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh-hk.facebook.com%2Fstudents.independence.union%2F&d=KChxWXaIVet3ZRtCu1MdJ0bB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=51e8ae43\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh-hk.facebook.com/students.independence.union/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/51214588_592559094520836_7481147574326394880_n.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=16e93169a001758b5d2115e091ca977b&amp;oe=5CF7AF02\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F51214588_592559094520836_7481147574326394880_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3D16e93169a001758b5d2115e091ca977b%26oe%3D5CF7AF02&h=574d89ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三年前嘅初一，義士們為咗守護旺角夜市高呼本土特色，勇武捍衛，犠牲了自己的未來，方有今日政府開始關注小販文化。<br />\n<br />\n二月四日晚九點，我們將會延續初一義士精神，到旺角夜市清潔街道以及守護熟食小販。<br />\n<br />\n香港獨立聯盟PayPal自由定額資助：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.paypal.me/hkindependenceunion\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.paypal.me%2Fhkindependenceunion&d=KChxWXaIVet3ZRtCu1MdJ0bB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=27b6c4a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.paypal.me/hkindependenceunion</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/cLGDY7PP/2019.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FcLGDY7PP%2F2019.jpg&h=7529aace&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f3061ea7aa52ba8a876cf79ae8deb38cad1026b5","tid":1008300,"uid":208726,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-